<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.8.7">
<l>vēmpiṉ puḻuvēm piṉṟiyuṇ ṇātaṭiyēṉ</l>
<l>nāṉpiṉ ṉumuṉcē vaṭiyaṉ ṟinayavēṉ</l>
<l>tēmpa liḷantiṅ kaḷciṟai viṭuttaivāyp</l>
<l>pāmpi ṉaṇaippaḷ ḷikoṇṭāy parañcōtī.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Without the neem tree, neem worms do not eat; moreover,</l>
<l>I, your servant, feel no longing without your bright feet,</l>
<l>You who, having  freed the thin, new moon from captivity,</l>
<l>Sleep on a five-headed serpent bed, supreme splendor.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
